title: BaBylissPRO Nano Titanium Straightening Iron
description: Ionic technology is perfectly paired with the benefits of pure titanium-plated plates for the smoothest, sleekest styles ever! Natural ions reduce frizz while the stay-cool Ryton housing resists the ultra-high heat for comfortable handling. The ceramic heater produces instant heat, up to 450°F, and fast heat recovery for styling efficiency with no damaging hot spots. Available in 1-1/4 inch and 1-3/4 inch plates.

title: BaByliss Pro BAB2000 Ceramix Xtreme  Dryer
description: Professional long-life motor with 6 speed/heat setting conbinations. Removable filter for easy cleaning. Narrow barrel for maximum air pressure.  Micro concentrator nozzle.
